    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const researchResult = $input.first().json;\nconst organic = researchResult.organic || [];\n\nconst research = organic.length > 0\n  ? organic.slice(0, 5).map(r => r.title + ': ' + r.snippet).join(' | ')\n  : 'No research available';\n\n// Lead data was carried into Research Company via Build Research Query\n// Read it back from that node since HTTP Request replaced $input\nconst lead = $('Build Research Query').first().json;\n\nconst prompt = `You are a B2B sales AI writing outreach on behalf of a salesperson.\n\nSENDER'S SERVICE: ${lead.yourService || 'consulting services'}\n\nLEAD: ${lead.fullName} at ${lead.domain || 'unknown company'}\nOUTREACH METHOD: ${lead.outreachMethod}\nRESEARCH: ${research}\n\nWrite a highly personalized outreach message. Respond ONLY with valid JSON, no extra text:\n{\n  \"score\": <integer 1-10>,\n  \"hooks\": [\"specific fact 1\", \"specific fact 2\"],\n  \"reasoning\": \"one sentence explaining score\",\n  \"subject\": \"email subject (empty string if linkedin)\",\n  \"body\": \"message body\"\n}\n\nRULES FOR BODY:\n- Start with \"Hi ${lead.firstName},\"\n- First sentence: reference ONE specific fact from research\n- Second sentence: connect that fact to a problem your service solves\n- Third sentence: mention the sender's service naturally\n- End with ONE specific question\n- Max 5 sentences for email, max 3 for LinkedIn\n- Never say \"our solutions\", \"stay ahead of the curve\", \"drive growth\"\n- Write as a peer, not a salesperson\n\nSCORING: 8-10=tech company with budget signals; 5-7=unclear fit; 1-4=local business`;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    ...lead,\n    research,\n    groqBody: JSON.stringify({\n      model: 'llama-3.1-8b-instant',\n      max_tokens: 600,\n      temperature: 0.3,\n      messages: [{ role: 'user', content: prompt }]\n    }),\n    researchBody: undefined\n  }\n}];"
      },
